%%%CALL
%%%VALGRIND
%%%DESCRIPTION Running without arguments
%%%OUTPUT
ERROR in Fraud3 parameters. Input file not provided
Run with the following arguments:
Fraud3 [-K <K>] [-o <outputFile.dts>] <inputFile.dts>

Parameters:
-K <K>: an integer with the number of clusters to use (5 by default)
-o <outputFile.dts>: name of the output dataset file (tests/output/output.dts by default)
<inputFile.dts>: name of the input dataset file
